        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Earrings are more than just accessories; they're an expression of individuality, elegance and personal style. Whether you prefer minimal studs or dramatic chandeliers, understanding earring types helps you choose the perfect pair for every occasion.</p><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, every piece tells a story of craftsmanship and conscious luxury. This guide will walk you through the most popular earring types, what makes them unique and how to choose the perfect style for your look and budget.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9cELiG": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. Stud Earrings -Simple, Timeless, and Elegant",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1. Stud Earrings -Simple, Timeless, and Elegant</h2>",
            "custom_id": "stud-earrings",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_C4KUKT": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1._Stud_Earrings_Simple_Timeless_and_Elegant.png",
            "text": "<p>Studs are the foundation of every j<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/jewelry\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/jewelry\">ewelry collection</a>. Sitting neatly on the earlobe, they’re perfect for everyday wear and ethnic looks. From classic diamonds to sleek metals, studs pair effortlessly with every outfit.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "cut",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "bezel-set-hexagon-diamond-earrings",
              "celestial-hex-diamond-stud-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If you appreciate minimalist beauty, explore the handcrafted designs from our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Collections</span></a>, where timeless elegance meets modern artistry.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_A8fUE6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2. Hoop Earrings – Versatile and Bold",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>2. Hoop Earrings – Versatile and Bold</h2>",
            "custom_id": "hoop",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ry4cQt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2._Hoop_Earrings_Versatile_and_Bold.png",
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/diamond-hoop-earrings\" title=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/diamond-hoop-earrings\">Diamond Hoop earrings </a>symbolize confidence and flair. Available in various sizes  from small, subtle circles to oversized statement hoops  they bring balance and sophistication to any outfit.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1-01-ct-pear-shaped-diamond-solitaire-stud-earrings",
              "6-prong-solitaire-stud-1-5-cts"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>For a warm toned twist, the soft hue of rose gold offers a modern charm. Discover that refined glow in our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> collection, a perfect complement to any hoop or minimalist earring ensemble.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. Drop Earrings – Effortlessly Graceful",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>3. Drop Earrings – Effortlessly Graceful</h2>",
            "custom_id": "drop",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_BiE3eV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3._Drop_Earrings_Effortlessly_Graceful.png",
            "text": "<p>Drop earrings hang slightly below the earlobe and move gently with every turn of your head. They’re ideal for adding understated elegance to both casual and evening looks.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "blue-majesty-gemstone-drop-earrings",
              "floral-halo-diamond-hoop-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> Depending on design, they can feature gemstones, pearls or even intricate metalwork.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Dangle Earrings - Dramatic and Expressive",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>4. Dangle Earrings - Dramatic and Expressive</h2>",
            "custom_id": "dangle",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XgNzg9": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4._Dangle_Earrings_Dramatic_and_Expressive.png",
            "text": "<p>For those who love a statement piece, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/dangles\" title=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/dangles\">dangle earrings</a> bring captivating movement and personality. From linear designs to ornate chandeliers, they exude confidence and sophistication.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "chainline-oval-diamond-dangle-earrings",
              "dual-halo-diamond-dangle-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7geBUB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lucira’s craftsmanship captures this artistic side of jewelry making where each design is as unique as the person wearing it.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_MqMKm8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Chandelier Earrings - Glamour at Its Finest",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>5. Chandelier Earrings - Glamour at Its Finest</h2>",
            "custom_id": "chandelier",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Npyztw": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5._Chandelier_Earrings_Glamour_at_Its_Finest.png",
            "text": "<p>Chandelier earrings are a classic choice for special occasions. With intricate tiers and brilliant sparkle, they frame the face beautifully and enhance formal attire. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_NyE7QP": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Their cascading structure makes them the centerpiece of any look, an instant way to make a statement at weddings or evening events.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Gd8BGb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Huggie Earrings  - Subtle Luxury for Everyday Wear",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>6. Huggie Earrings  - Subtle Luxury for Everyday Wear</h2>",
            "custom_id": "huggie",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_nnUCCQ": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/6._Huggie_Earrings_Subtle_Luxury_for_Everyday_Wear.png",
            "text": "<p>Huggie earrings are smaller hoops that “hug” the earlobe closely. They’re ideal for daily wear, comfortable yet chic and available in polished metals or diamond studded designs.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "classic-diamond-huggie-earrings",
              "emerald-cut-and-round-diamond-huggie-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_L8CGqm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>To experience Lucira’s craftsmanship in small-scale brilliance, explore our elegant lab grown diamond necklace range, each piece embodying the same understated luxury that defines huggie earrings.  </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UirriL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "7. Choosing the Right Earring for Your Face Shape",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>7. Choosing the Right Earring for Your Face Shape</h2>",
            "custom_id": "choosing",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_EVfxcf": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8._Choosing_the_Right_Earring_for_Your_Face_Shape_79850cdc-b3d1-4606-ad1f-ff97717f3e9f.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bpNHRT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Round Face: Go for elongated styles like drop or dangle earrings to add length.</li><li>Oval Face: Most shapes flatter this face type - try hoops or huggies.</li><li>Square Face: Choose round or curved designs to soften angles.</li><li>Heart-Shaped Face: Chandeliers or teardrop styles balance the jawline beautifully.</li></ul><p>At Lucira, you can find designs that complement every face shape and personality all crafted to perfection using sustainable, lab-grown diamonds.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ETM9ET": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "8. Lab-Grown Diamond Earrings – The Ethical Choice",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>8. Lab-Grown Diamond Earrings – The Ethical Choice</h2>",
            "custom_id": "lab-grown",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_LwwtwE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9._Lab-Grown_Diamond_Earrings_The_Ethical_Choice.png",
            "text": "<p>Lab-grown diamond earrings combine brilliance with conscience. They’re physically and chemically identical to mined diamonds but more affordable and environmentally responsible.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Q3YK9p": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>To compare their value, view the 1 carat lab grown diamond price in India and see how innovation meets ethics without compromising beauty. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_C6b9cw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9. Visit Lucira’s Boutique for  a Personalized Experience",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>9. Visit Lucira’s Boutique for  a Personalized Experience</h2>",
            "custom_id": "visit",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_KadCcG": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Choosing the perfect earrings is personal and seeing them in person can make all the difference.<br/>If you’re in Mumbai, step into the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur Lucira Store</span></a> to explore our curated jewelry displays and speak with our experts for styling advice.</p><p>From timeless studs to contemporary ear cuffs, our collection celebrates individuality with every sparkle.</p><p>Redefine your style with earrings that speak to your elegance and individuality.Explore <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira’s</span></a> full Collections online or visit our Chembur boutique to experience luxury that shines with conscience.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
